                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">Codebase &amp; Infrastructure Analysis</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">8 to 12 hours of hands-on review, done by me, not delegated.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 border border-sf-border bg-sf-black card-hover animate-on-scroll stagger-1">
