                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 border border-sf-border bg-sf-black card-hover animate-on-scroll stagger-3">
                    <span class="font-display text-3xl text-sf-red leading-none flex-shrink-0">04</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">Architecture Scoring</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">Scored across four dimensions: ability to grow, maintainability, security, and performance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 border border-sf-border bg-sf-black card-hover animate-on-scroll stagger-4">
                    <span class="font-display text-3xl text-sf-red leading-none flex-shrink-0">05</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">Executive Presentation &amp; Report</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">A 1-hour executive summary plus a full written report your board can read and your team can reference.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 border border-sf-border bg-sf-black card-hover animate-on-scroll stagger-4">
                    <span class="font-display text-3xl text-sf-red leading-none flex-shrink-0">06</span>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-1">30-60-90 Day Action Plan</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">Estimated effort and expected results for each recommendation. Start executing on Monday morning.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- 04 — RESULTS                                                  -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <section class="relative py-24 lg:py-32" aria-label="Results">
        <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <p class="font-display text-sm tracking-[4px] text-sf-red mb-3">04</p>
                <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight">What Changes <span class="text-sf-muted">After the Assessment</span></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-sf-border animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="bg-sf-surface p-8 text-center">
                    <div class="font-display text-5xl text-sf-red leading-none mb-2">60%</div>
