                    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide mb-3">New Technical Leaders</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">You inherited this codebase. You need an honest picture before you commit to a direction or make promises to the board.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border border-sf-border bg-sf-surface-light card-hover animate-on-scroll stagger-3">
                    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl tracking-wide mb-3">Non-Technical Founders</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-sf-muted leading-relaxed">You sense something is wrong but need a translator between engineering reality and business decisions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

